data.title: Washburn University School of Law
data.meta_description: Washburn University School of Law in Topeka, Kansas. Information for prospective students, current students, and alumni. Washburn Law offers a spring start program so you can start law school in January during the spring semester. Home of the Washburn Law Journal and WashLaw Web.
data.text:
"If I could redo my law school career, I would choose Washburn again. I always felt valued and respected by staff, lecturers, and professors, and am especially grateful for Washburn's rigorous legal writing program that has given me the tools to be a strong advocate."

Recognized by The National Jurist as one of the Top Law Students in the Nation, 2019.

Jennifer Salva, '19, Washburn University Read More
